  "texts": [
    "The dimension of the maxpooling layers is set to 85, and its specific parameters for the Maxpooling Layer are recorded in Table 3.",
    "Drug-drug interaction predictionWe extracted the sequence and substructure information of drug-pair by Drug Substructure Graph Feature Encoder and Drug Molecule Sequence Feature Extraction module, respectively.",
    "We concatenate the extracted sequence and substructure information (13) MixAttention(D 1, D 2, D 2) =Concat(head 1,..., head 4), (14) head i =Attention D 1 W D 1 i, D 2 W D 2 i, D 2 W D 2 i.",
    "(15) Attention(D 1, D 2, D 2) = softmax( D 1 * D 2 T √ d * D 2),(16)Y out =concat Y 1, Y 2, (17) Y i =maxpooling Z i * 0.5 + MixAttention i * 0.5,in the prediction module, obtaining a final feature vector.",
    "This vector is then fed into a fully connected layer for the ultimate drug relationship prediction, thereby achieving the fusion of sequence and substructure information."
